{"tid":2027444,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"其實有幾多人唔知Google Outline VPN 唔係VPN 而係Shadowsocks?","createTime":"2020-05-21T11:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T04:39:08.000Z","uid":88743,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ea55c3a5e482adc54d1d8c19175986b54fd21df9","tid":2027444,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:38:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Outline_VPN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FOutline_VPN&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVwfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=96989d96\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Outline_VPN</a><br />\n<br />\nOutline VPN是一個自由及開放原始碼軟體，用於在多個雲服務上快速部署Shadowsocks伺服器<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>安全和隱私</ins></strong><br />\nOutline<span style=\"color: red;\">不是一個匿名工具</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>評價</ins></strong><br />\n2018年3月，PCMag（英語：PCMag）的Max Eddy表示，Outline VPN的預覽版本「非常容易使用（startlingly easy to use）」以及「消除了與VPN公司相關的隱私問題（removes privacy concerns associated with VPN companies）」。然而，<span style=\"color: red;\">Eddy批評該軟體沒有加密Windows上的所有流量，並警告用戶「與大型VPN公司相比，個人使用可能缺乏一些匿名性</span>（individual use may lack some anonymity compared [to] large VPN companies）」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSS 係大陸人所創，目的係用黎翻牆，唔係用黎匿名<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\noutline VPN 個膽係SS 我唔知佢改成點，但一定唔係VPN<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shadowsocks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FShadowsocks&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVwfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=478aedb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shadowsocks</a><br />\n<br />\nShadowsocks（簡稱SS）是一種基於Socks5代理方式的加密傳輸協定，也可以指實現這個協定的各種開發包。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>安全性</ins></strong><br />\nShadowsocks本質上只是設定了密碼的網路代理協定，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不能替代TLS或者VPN，不能用作匿名通信方案</span></span></strong>，該協定的目標不在於提供完整的通信安全機制，主要是為了協助上網用戶在嚴苛的網路環境中突破封鎖。不過，在匿名通信能夠被辨識或封鎖的情況下，<ins>也可將Shadowsocks與其他匿名方案<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">配合使用</span></span></strong></ins>，同時滿足突破封鎖和匿名的需求。"},{"pid":"58d0d5781fa2fb76e5f369c4d5142d99386e46bd","tid":2027444,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gLBp9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gLBp9Z.jpg&h=b5c1741c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a523418ac79883c3ddcbaf026f066101dcc005f5","tid":2027444,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:48:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a1fa3a3c42e784698f1546170d4dbec5432523d","tid":2027444,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6e4170db028532981962856e25d300dd1f54ee16","tid":2027444,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:27:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e15a208608bb00f032c065275555f6947a2fb208","tid":2027444,"uid":31719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:33:03.000Z","msg":"[免費安全]自己VPN 自己SET!!! (Google Cloud)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2027151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2027151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n佢一定唔知"},{"pid":"fe2ad184da1460e96b353bcade7269a20da6d5ef","tid":2027444,"uid":326725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"Hkgetv都用緊喎"},{"pid":"548d97e19c5695858cdade0c81421ab656606bd9","tid":2027444,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe2ad184da1460e96b353bcade7269a20da6d5ef","tid":2027444,"uid":326725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"Hkgetv都用緊喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:07:05.000Z","msg":"佢地都知係based on ss<br />\n佢地照用我都無計